<P>THE DOCTRINE OF PARTICULAR ELECTION AND FINAL PERSEVERANCE, EXPLAINED and VINDICATED. By I&s;aac Backus, PASTOR OF A CHURCH IN MIDDLEBOROUGH.</P>
<Q><L>Yea, let God be true, but every Man a Liar.&mdash;</L>
<L>The Election obtained it, and the Re&s;t were blinded.</L>
<BIBL><HI>Rom. iii. 4. xi. 7.</HI></BIBL></Q>
